Amy initially had 4 music files and 21 video files on her flash drive. The total number of files on her flash drive was 4 + 21 = <<4+21=25>>25 files.
Amy deleted 23 files, so the number of files remaining on her flash drive is 25 - 23 = <<25-23=2>>2 files. Therefore, there were 2 files still on her flash drive. 

